                                "text": "4L",
                                "style": {
                                    "code": true
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": ".\n\nI've also tweaked the testing code from a previous comment to also provide\ninformation about mouse x\/y coordinates to help verify that the patched code\npreserves (x,y) mouse coordinate conventions when the various events are\ntriggered:\n\n"
                            }
                        ]
